# WebPage.BackForwardList.Item

**Structure**

A representation of a resource that a webpage previously visited.

## Declaration

```swift
struct Item
```

## Overview

Two items with equal titles, urls, and initial urls may not necessarily be equal to one another.

## Structures

- **WebPage.BackForwardList.Item.ID**: An opaque type representing the identifier for an item.

## Instance Properties

- **id**: The unique identifier for the item.
- **initialURL**: The source URL that originally asked to load the resource.
- **title**: The title of the page this item represents.
- **url**: The url of the page this item represents, after having resolved all redirects.

## Conforms To

- Equatable
- Identifiable
- Sendable
- SendableMetatype
